                  <additions>
                     <p>
                        <locus n="1r">Folio 1r</locus> contains various notes on amounts of money
                        paid and transferred, scattered throughout the page; a deliberately erased
                        ownership inscription, several verses and two hadith. </p>
                     <p>
                        <locus n="135r">Folio 135r</locus> records a birth with a verse and ghazals
                        by a poet <persName role="aut" key="person_f8435">Luṭfī</persName>. folio 135v has verses
                        added, one by the same Luṭfī. </p>
                     <p>
                        <locus n="135v">Folio 135v</locus> contains a text about the religious
                        necessity of submitting to authorities. </p>
                  </additions>
